**who —** The Knacks — the everyday folk-magic of this America — one small, real power per person (fire, finding, fitting, hexing); the text frames the traditions as differing by people and heritage

**what —** the everyday folk-magic of this America — one small, real power per person (fire, finding, fitting, hexing); the text frames the traditions as differing by people and heritage

